<p><strong><br/></strong></p><p><strong>17th August 2009</strong></p><p>THE WHITTAWER SUMMER JUST KEEPS ON GETTING BETTER AND WE HAVE HAD TWO GREAT SHOWS AT THE CLA GAME FAIR AND THE GATCOMBE HORSE TRIALS WHERE SOME WELL KNOWN FACES WERE WEARING THEIR NEW WHITTAWER CLOTHES WITH PRIDE!! THE LATEST ADDITION TO THE WHITTAWER TEAM IS A 10 WEEK OLD BLACK LAB CALLED OSCAR WHO PROVED A BIG HIT AT GATCOMBE SO LOOK OUT FOR US AND HIM AT OUR NEXT COUPLE OF SHOWS IN SEPTEMBER....BURGHLEY AND BLENHEIM HORSE TRIALS.</p><p><br/></p><p></p><div style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 481px; height: 336px;" title="" alt=""  src="/images/5332_562059923021_277000315_4013598_2971219_n.jpg" align="baseline" border="0"/><br/></div><p><strong></strong></p><p><br/><strong></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><img style="width: 268px; height: 358px;" title="" alt=""  src="/images/5332_562059908051_277000315_4013595_4439372_n.jpg" align="baseline" border="0"/><br/></strong></p><p><strong><br/></strong></p><p><br/><strong></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-weight: normal;">WE ARE PLANNING A BANK HOLIDAY ROADTRIP IN OUR FAITHFUL VAN "DAVETTE" TO ROCK AND SALCOMBE WITH PARTIES AND A SUMMER SALE ORGANISED AT BOTH .... (VENUES AND DATES TO BE CONFIRMED IN NEXT 48 HRS) .... SO COME AND JOIN US FOR A GLASS OF PIMMS IF YOU AROUND.</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-weight: normal;">THE NEW UNIVERSITY YEAR IS UPON US ONCE AGAIN AND THE WHITTAWER TEAM WILL BE EMBARKING ON A MONTH LONG TOUR AROUND THE COUNTRY VISITING AROUND 15 UNIVERSITIES INCLUDING EXETER, NOTTINGHAM, OXFORD, DURHAM, NEWCASTLE, EDINBURGH, CARDIFF, RAC, BROOKES, LEEDS, LAMPETER, NORTHUMBRIA, BRISTOL, BATH, AND READING TO NAME A FEW...KEEP CHECKING THE WEBSITE FOR SPECIFIC DATES AT EACH UNI!!</span><br/></strong></p><p><strong><br/></strong></p><p><strong>22nd July 2009<br/></strong><br/>WHITTAWER ARE NOW THE OFFICIAL CLOTHING SPONSER OF CRAZY LARRYS!!! FOR MORE INFORMATION ON CLUB NIGHTS HELD AT CRAZY LARRYS, PLEASE VISIT <a href="http://www.crazylarrys.co.uk">www.crazylarrys.co.uk</a>. HERE ARE SOME PHOTOS OF LARRYS IN ACTION..........<br/><br/><img style="width: 356px; height: 273px; cursor: pointer;" onClick="return Control.invoke('ReadingPane', '_onAttachmentClick', event);" alt="" src="http://co113w.col113.mail.live.com/att/GetAttachment.aspx?tnail=2&messageId=4c354f44-26ff-4cf4-a439-7df6bc17149e&Aux=4%7C0%7C8CBD8F9F74D9600%7C" height="402" width="604"/><br/><br/><img style="width: 385px; height: 294px; cursor: pointer;" onClick="return Control.invoke('ReadingPane', '_onAttachmentClick', event);" alt="" src="http://co113w.col113.mail.live.com/att/GetAttachment.aspx?tnail=3&messageId=4c354f44-26ff-4cf4-a439-7df6bc17149e&Aux=4%7C0%7C8CBD8F9F74D9600%7C" height="402" width="604"/><br/><br/><img style="width: 317px; height: 273px; cursor: pointer;" onClick="return Control.invoke('ReadingPane', '_onAttachmentClick', event);" alt="" src="http://co113w.col113.mail.live.com/att/GetAttachment.aspx?tnail=0&messageId=4c354f44-26ff-4cf4-a439-7df6bc17149e&Aux=4%7C0%7C8CBD8F9F74D9600%7C" height="402" width="604"/><br/><br/><br/><img style="width: 329px; height: 267px; cursor: pointer;" onClick="return Control.invoke('ReadingPane', '_onAttachmentClick', event);" alt="" src="http://co113w.col113.mail.live.com/att/GetAttachment.aspx?tnail=1&messageId=4c354f44-26ff-4cf4-a439-7df6bc17149e&Aux=4%7C0%7C8CBD8F9F74D9600%7C" height="402" width="604"/><br/><br/><br/><strong>12.06.09- 22.07.09</strong></p>
<p>THE WHITTAWER TEAM HAVE BEEN OUT AND ABOUT ACROSS THE COUNTRY OVER THE LAST FEW WEEKS.....SETTING UP TRADE STANDS AT THE EAST OF ENGLAND SHOW, HENLEY REGATTA AND THE NORFOLK SHOW HAS BEEN A GREAT OPPORTUNITY FOR US TO SPREAD THE WHITTAWER NAME AS WELL AS PUT A FEW MORE MILES UNDER "DAVETTE'S" BELT!! <br/><br/>AS WELL AS THIS, THE NEW LIMITED EDITION SUMMER RANGE HAS JUST ARRIVED AND WILL BE ON SALE SHORTLY SO MAKE THE MOST OF THE SUMMER WITH SOME NEW CLOTHES!! <br/><br/>ALSO, KEEP AN EYE OUT FOR US AT THE GAME FAIR IN GRANTHAM AT THE END OF THIS WEEK- PLENTY OF DEALS TO BE HAD ON OUR GREAT RANGE OF LEISUREWEAR!!<br/><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br/><br/><br/>10th JUNE TO THE 13th JUNE<br/><br/></span></span></span></span>THIS SAW THE TEAM EMBARK ON A MINI UNIVERSITIES TOUR AROUND NOTTINGHAM, DURHAM AND EDINBURGH. &nbsp;SADLY 'DAVETTE' WAS NOT ABLE TO JOIN US ON THE TOUR AND ALTHOUGH SHE HAD A NEW LEASE OF LIFE WITH A NEW ENGINE, SHE STILL HAD A MAJOR OIL LEAK THAT COULD NOT BE FOUND AND FIXED IN TIME. &nbsp;HOWEVER WE ARE PLEASED TO ANNOUNCE THAT SHE IS ONCE AGAIN FIGHTING FIT AND WILL BE AT AN EVENT NEAR YOU!!!!! <br/><br/>SADLY DUE TO THE VAN NOT BEING READY IN TIME, NOTTINGHAM HAD TO BE PUSHED BACK TWO WEEKS. &nbsp;AS A RESULT OUR TRIP COMMENCED WITH A WHITTAWER PARTY IN KULTE NIGHTCLUB IN DURHAM. &nbsp;THERE WERE LOTS IN ATTENDANCE WITH LOTS OF GIVEAWAYS. &nbsp;THE THURSDAY SAW US AT THE CRICKET GROUND SHOWING OFF OUR CLOTHES TO THE ADORNING PUBLIC. &nbsp;SADLY AS ALWAYS WHEN CRICKET IS ON, IT RAINED AND AS A RESULT THE MATCH WAS CALLED OFF.<br/><br/>FOLLOWING ON FROM DURHAM, THE TRIP HEADED NORTH TO EDINBURGH FOR ANOTHER NIGHT OF CALAMATIES. &nbsp;THIS TIME WE WERE AT THE OPAL LOUNGE ON ST GEORGE STREET. &nbsp;THE NIGHT WAS VERY BUSY AS WE WERE LOOKING FOR POTENTIAL MODELS FOR OUR NEXT LINE. &nbsp;ONCE AGAIN THERE WERE NUMEROUS GIVEAWAYS TOGETHER WITH 'GAMBIT LIVE' WHO HELPED US WITH THE WHOLE EVENT. &nbsp;<br/><br/>IF YOU THINK YOU HAVE WHAT IT TAKES TO BE A MODEL FOR US THEN EMAIL INFO@WHITTAWER.CO.UK AND WE WILL BE HAPPY TO SEE WHAT YOU CAN OFFER!!!<br/><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><br/>07th JUNE <br/><br/><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span></span></span></span>THE VARSITY POLO MATCH AT KIRKLINGTON POLO CLUB<br/><br/>WE HAD A GREAT DAY WITH LOTS OF SUNSHINE AND A WIN FOR THE OXFORD POLO TEAM. &nbsp;GOOD THING AS WE ARE THE SPONSORS OF THE OXFORD POLO TEAM!! &nbsp;THE WINNING SCORE WAS OXFORD 6, CAMBRIDGE 2. &nbsp;THE TRADESTAND WENT DOWN A STORM WITH LOTS OF INTEREST AND LOTS AND LOTS OF SALES. &nbsp;THIS WAS THE FIRST OUTING OF OUR BRAND NEW LINE OF GILLETS. &nbsp; PLEASE VISIT THE WEBSITE FOR MORE DETAILS.<span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><br/></span><br/>30th AND 31st OF MAY<br/><br/><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><span style="font-weight: bold;">CASTLE ASHBY</span></span><br/><br/></span></span>WHITTAWER WERE AT THE CASTLE ASHBY GAME FAIR. &nbsp;IT WAS A VERY DRUNKEN AND SUCCESSFUL WEEKEND FOR WHITTAWER AS WE WERE PLACED, ONCE AGAIN, NEXT TO THE BEER TENT!!!!! &nbsp;A PERK THAT IS ALWAYS GOOD FOR BUSINESS!! &nbsp;LUCKILY IT WAS VERY SUNNY FOR BOTH DAYS AND A GOOD TIME WAS HAD BY ALL. &nbsp;PICTURES COMING SOON.<br/><br/></p>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img title="" alt=""  src="src=" align="baseline" border="0" height="1024" width="768"/><br/></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 232px; height: 287px;" title="" alt=""  src="src=" images="" jpg="" align="baseline" border="0"/><br/></div><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><br/>24th AND 25th OF MAY</span><br/><br/>WHITTAWER ONCE AGAIN WAS IN ATTENDANCE OF THE LAST FEW REMAINING POINT TO POINTS OF THE SEASON. &nbsp;SADLY WE WERE ONCE AGAIN WITHOUT OUR BELOVED CAMPER VAN DAVE. &nbsp;SHE IS SADLY STILL IN THE GARAGE HAVING AN ENGINE TRANSPLANT BUT WILL BE BACK WITH US VERY VERY SOON. &nbsp;IF YOU ARE GOING TO BE AT THE VARSITY POLO MATCH, KEEP AN EYE OUT, SHE WILL BE THERE!!!<br/><br/>SUNDAY WE SET UP STALL AT THE KINGSTON BLOUNT POINT TO POINT. &nbsp;ACCORDING TO PREIVOUS RECORDS, THE EVENT HAS BEEN A WASH OUT FOR THE PAST 4 YEARS. &nbsp;NOT THIS YEAR! &nbsp;THE SUN WAS SHINING PEOPLE WERE HAPPY AND THE POLO SHIRTS FLEW OFF THE SHELF. &nbsp;THANK YOU TO ALL THOSE WHO VISITED THE STAND IN SUPPORT WEATHER JUST BROWSING OR BUYING.<br/><br/>MONDAY WAS OUR FIRST VISIT TO THE CHADDESLEY-CORBETT POINT TO POINT IN HEREFORDSHIRE. &nbsp;THIS IS ONE WE WILL MOST CERTIANLY BE ATTENDING AGAIN NEXT YEAR. &nbsp;THE DAY STARTED OFF SLOWLY. &nbsp;ALL DAY IT LOOKED AS THOUGH THE RAIN WAS GOING TO RUIN IT FOR EVERYONE. &nbsp;LUCKILY THE WEATHER WORKED IN OUR ADVANTAGE. &nbsp;THE HOODIES AND TRACKIES FLEW OFF THE SHELF.<br/><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">NOTE FOR THE FUTURE: IF YOU SEE US AT AN EVENTS COME AND ASK ABOUT OUR ON THE DAY DEALS!!!!<br/><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br/>MANY THANKS TO JULIAN KING AND HIS BUNCH OF MERRY MUCKERS WHO SO PROUDLY ADVERTISED OUR KNICKERS FOR US. &nbsp;IF YOU HAVE PICTURES SEND THEM IN!<br/><br/>THE DAY ENDED IN BEING A HUGE SUCCESS. &nbsp;MANY THANK TO ALL THOSE WHO CAME. &nbsp;<br/><br/>FUTURE EVENTS TO COME TO KEEP A LOOK OUT FOR: &nbsp;<br/>07.02.09: VARSITY POLO MATCH<br/>JUNE: UNIVERSITIES TOUR<br/>JULY: ROYAL NORFOLK SHOW, HENLEY REGATTA, CARTIER AND VEUVE CLIQUOT POLO AND MANY MORE!!!<br/><br/></span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;">22.05.09<br/><br/><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">WHITTAWER ATTENDS THE CIREN VS EXETER POLO MATCH<br/><br/><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">WE ARE PROUD TO ANNOUNCE THAT WE ARE THE OFFICIAL SPONSORS FOR THE EXETER POLO TEAM</span></span><br/><br/></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">FRIDAY THE 22ND SAW WHITTAWER ATTEND ITS FIRST POLO MEET. &nbsp;THE DAY SAW THE MATCH BETWEEN THE CIRENCESTER ROYAL AGRICULTURAL COLLEGE POLO TEAM AND THE EXETER POLO TEAM. &nbsp;WE ARE PLEASED TO ANNOUNCE THAT WE ARE THE PROUD SPONSORS OF THE EXETER POLO TEAM. &nbsp;<br/>ALTHOUGH THE DAY WAS WINDY, THE RAIN HELD OFF. &nbsp;THE MATCH WAS FAST AND AGRESSIVE WITH SOME VERY GOOD GOALS. &nbsp;THE SCORES FOLLOWED EACH OTHER THROUGH OUT THE MATCH WITH BOTH TEAMS TAKING QUARTERLY LEADS. &nbsp;AFTER A CLOSE MATCH THE END SCORES WERE 61/2 GOALS TO 6, RAC BEING THE WINNERS. &nbsp;<br/><br/>OUR MAN AT THE GROUND WAS LUCKY ENOUGH TO PRESENT THE PRIZES TO BOTH TEAMS. &nbsp;PHOTOS WILL BE COMING SOON!!!!!<br/></span></span><br/>&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr>
<td style="font-family: tahoma;"><strong><span style="font-weight: bold;">19.05.09<br/><br/><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153);">WHITTAWER SPONSORS OXFORD UNIVERSITY VARSITY POLO TEAM!!!<br/></span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153);"></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-weight: normal;"><br/><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">WE ARE REALLY PROUD TO ANNOUNCE THAT <span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">WHITTAWER</span> WILL BE THE TITLE SPONSOR OF THE <span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">OXFORD UNIVERSITY VARSITY POLO TEAM</span>. OUR LOGO WILL BE ACROSS THE TEAMS PLAYING AND WARM UP KIT, WE WILL ALSO BE HOLDING A TRADE STAND AT THE VARSITY MATCH. THE MATCH IS BEING PLAYED ON <span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">SUNDAY 7TH JUNE 2009 AT KIRLINGTON PARK POLO CLUB.</span> IF YOU ARE GOING TO THERE PLEASE COME AND SEE US AT OUR <span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">WHITTAWER TRADE STAND AND HOSPITALITY TENT.</span> THERE WILL BE LOTS OF PROMOTIONS ON ALL OF OUR WHITTAWER CLOTHES. HOPE TO SEE YOU THERE AND BEST OF LUCK TO OXFORD UNIVERISTY POLO TEAM!!!</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 153);"><br/></span></span></span></span><br/><br style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal;">********************************************************************************************************************</span><br style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal;">********************************************************************************************************************</span><br/><br/>05.05.09<br/><br/></strong><font color="#000099"><strong>WHITTAWER AT DINGLEY POINT TO POINT<br/><br/></strong><font color="#000000">WHITTAWER SPENT THE WEEKEND AT DINGLEY POINT TO POINT. SADLY "DAVE" THE CAMPER VAN IS STILL IN A GARAGE IN FRANCE SO COULDN'T MAKE IT! DESPITE THIS WE HAD A GREAT, IF NOT A BIT WINDY DAY AT THE RACES. THERE WAS LOTS OF INTEREST IN ALL THE CURRENT CLOTHES AND LOADS OF&nbsp;EXCITEMENT IN THE<font color="#ff0000"> LIMITED EDITION SUMMER RANGE </font>THAT IS COMING SOON!!!<br/><br/>A BIG THANK YOU GOES TO ALL OF YOU WHO CAME TO SEE US ON OUR STAND, ESPECALLY THE GENTLEMEN WHO CAME WITH A BOTTLE OF IPA FOR ME AND JAMES!!<br/><br/>WE WILL BE AT ANOTHER POINT TO POINT THIS MONTH SO KEEP CHECKING THE BLOG AND FACEBOOK FOR MORE DETAILS!!<br/><br/>*******************************************************************************************************************<br/>*******************************************************************************************************************<br/><br/></font><br/><strong><font color="#000000">24.04.09<br/></font><br/></strong><font color="#000099"><font color="#000000"><font color="#000099"><strong>BREAKING NEWS: WHITTAWER ARE RELEASING A LIMITED EDITION SUMMER RANGE!!!<br/><br/></strong></font><font color="#000000">AFTER HUNDREDS OF DRAWING, HOURS OF MEETINGS AND MORE PROCRASTINATION THAN IS HEALTHY THE WHITTAWER DESIGN TEAM HAVE FINALISED THE DESIGNS FOR THE NEW RANGES OF CLOTHES!!!!!!!<br/><br/>WE ARE REALLY HAPPY TO ANNOUNCE THAT WE WILL HAVE A <font color="#ff0000">LIMITED EDITION SUMMER RANGE </font>THAT WILL CONSISTED OF <font color="#ff0000">GIRLS FITTED T SHIRTS, BOY T-SHIRTS, GILETS AND CAPS</font> THAT WILL BE HERE BY&nbsp;THE END OF MAY. IF YOU WAN TO GET YOUR HANDS ON THIS LIMITED EDITION RANGE&nbsp;COME TO THE SHOP IN OXFORD, LOG ONTO THE&nbsp;WEBSITE OR COME AND SEE US AT HENLEY ROYAL REGATTA AND THE NORFOLK SHOW.&nbsp;<br/><br/>ALSO COMING IN THE SUMMER IS <font color="#ff0000">TRACKIES TYPE SHORTS AND ZIP UP HOODIES</font> WE HOPE TO HAVE THESE IN STOCK BY THE BEGINNING OF JULY!!</font><br/></font><br/><br/><font color="#000000">******************************************************************************************************************</font><br/><font color="#000000">******************************************************************************************************************</font><br/><br/><br/></font><strong>22.04.09<br/><br/></strong><font color="#000099"><strong>WHITTAWER WINTER TOUR 2009<br/><br/></strong></font><font color="#000099">
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Tahoma','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 8.5pt;">MYSELF, JAMES, BEANIE AND ARCHIE THE CAMERA MAN, HAVE JUST RETURNED FROM <font size="+0"><font size="+0">10</font></font> DAYS OF <font size="+0"><font size="+0">WHITTAWER</font></font> FUN IN VAL <font size="+0"><font size="+0">D'ISERE</font></font>, <font size="+0"><font size="+0">VERBIER</font></font> AND <font size="+0"><font size="+0">CHAMONIX</font></font>. WE WERE BLESSED WITH THE HOLY GRAIL OF GOOD SNOW AND GOOD WEATHER ALL WEEK!! BUT IT WASN'T ALL FUN THERE WAS LOTS OF HARD WORK TO BE DONE SPREADING THE <font size="+0"><font size="+0">WHITTAWER</font></font> LOVE THROUGHOUT ALPS!<br/></span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Tahoma','sans-serif'; color: rgb(0, 0, 153); font-size: 8.5pt;"><br/></span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Tahoma','sans-serif'; color: black; font-size: 8.5pt;"><font size="+0"><font size="+0">WHITTAWER</font></font> HOSTED PARTIES AT BANANAS BAR, LE <font size="+0"><font size="+0">FOLIE</font></font> <font size="+0"><font size="+0">DOUCE</font></font>, SALOON BAR, MORRIS PUB AND T BAR. WE ALL WANT TO SAY A MASSIVE THANK YOU TO ALL THE STAFF WHO WORKED HARD TO PROVIDE EVERYONE WITH.............REFRESHMENTS AND LOOKED SO GOOD IN THE <font size="+0"><font size="+0">WHITTAWER</font></font> CLOTHES, ESPECIALLY THE MORRIS PUB GIRLS!! (SEE PHOTO)<br/><br/></span></p></font><font color="#000099">
