<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="left">******************************************************************************************************************<br/>******************************************************************************************************************<br/><br/><br/><strong>13.04.09<br/></strong><br/><strong><font color="#000099">LOCKINGE POINT TO POINT<br/></font></strong><br/>WHITTAWER HAD THEIR FIRST GO AT HOLDING A TRADE STAND AT A POINT TO POINT THIS EASTER MONDAY. THE DAY, WHICH GOT OFF TO A SLOW START, WHERE EVERYTING THAT&nbsp;COULD HAVE&nbsp;WRONG WENT WRONG, ENDED UP BEING A HUGE SUCCESS!!!<br/><br/>IF YOU WERE AMONG THE 15,000 PEOPLE AT LOCKINGE POINT TO POINT AND YOU CAME TO SEE US THANK YOU VERY MUCH. WE SET UP A LITTLE STAND ON WHAT CAN ONLY BE DESCRIBED AS A&nbsp;MOUNTAIN AND DID OUR BEST TO KEEP SPADING THE WHITTAWER LOVE!! THE DAY WAS SUCH A SUCCESS WE HAVE BOOKED IN TO DO 2 MORE POINT TO POINTS. WE ARE GOING TO BE AT.....<br/><br/>FERNIE HUNT POINT TO POINT AT DINGLEY RACECOURSE ON SUNDAY 3RD MAY<br/><br/>SURREY UNION POINT TO POINT ON&nbsp;SATURDAY 9TH MAY<br/><br/></p>
